# Ignore artifacts output
# If models/ is generated strictly in dev, you might ignore it, 
# but usually we want to bundle the models in our production image.
# Do NOT ignore models/ or data/ entirely, wait we DO need them inside.
# But we might ignore specific huge datasets if not required for inference.
# ml/assets/ can be ignored if it's just plots.
ml/assets/
